content.label: Introduction
Welcome! Thank you for participating in this survey. Your feedback is valuable in helping us improve our products and services. This survey should take approximately 5-7 minutes to complete.
Do you consent to participate in this survey?
Yes
No
Screening
Have you purchased a product from us in the last 6 months?
What is your age range?
What is your gender?
Product Satisfaction
How satisfied are you with the following aspects of the product you purchased?
What is the primary reason for your satisfaction or dissatisfaction with the product quality?
How likely are you to recommend the product to a friend or colleague?
Why did you select that rating?
Customer Service Experience
Have you contacted our customer service team in the past 6 months?
How satisfied are you with the following aspects of your customer service experience?
What was the main reason for contacting customer service?
If you were dissatisfied with the customer service experience, what could we have done to improve it?
Overall Brand Perception
Please rate your agreement with the following statements:
Which of the following words best describe our brand? (Select all that apply)
What is one thing we could do to improve your overall perception of our brand?
Conclusion
Thank you for your valuable feedback. Your responses will help us improve our products and services.
